snippet.title: The CyberClash Is On! Clash of Clans New Season
snippet.description:
Corrupt megacorps and freedom-fighting Renegades battle for control of a neon-soaked dystopia! The CyberClash is on! Gear up with cybernetic Hero Skins and take a side in this battle of might and metal. Explore the Cyber Scenery and add some holographic hijinks to your Home Village. A whole host of epic Events and offers await this Season! 

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Song 1 :
Anak lanang kudu iso, nyonggo abote donyo
(Anak laki-laki harus bisa, menyangga beban dunia)
Kabeh ora ngandalke wong tuo
(Semuanya tidak harus mengandalkan orang tua)
Tabungan ora sepiro, Sangu mung restu lan dongo
(Tabungan tidak seberapa, bekal hanyalah restu dan doa)
ngadepi pacoban sing teko
(Hadapi cobaan yang datang)

Turu dewe bapak cen jarang ngancani
(Tidur sendiri bapak memang jarang menemani)
Nglilir Tengah wengi bapak durung bali
(Terbangun dimalam hari bapak belum pulang)
Soyo gedi soyo ngerti 
(Semakin besar semakin mengerti)
abote golek rejeki sing halal sing iso mberkahi
(Beratnya mencari rezeki yang halal dan membawa berkah)

Reff :
Lanange jagad dadio koyo arjuno
(Laki - laki dunia jadilah seperti Arjuna)
Rakakean crito susah seneng adepono
(Tak banyak bercerita susah senang dihadapi)
Ngger anak ku lanang golek o pepadange dalan
(Nak, anakku laki laki carilah jalan yang terang)
Ora terus tak kudang dadio lanang tenan
(Tidak harusku timang, jadilah laki-laki yang sebenarnya)

Song 2
Bapak ibuk ngusahakke, mboh pie carane
(Bapak ibu akan mengusahakan apapun caranya)
Raperlu melu ngrasakke rekasane
(Tak perlu merasakan susahnya)
Omah mewah mepet sawah
(Rumah mewah mepet sawah)
Ora kudu wah, penting cukup kadang yo turah
(Tidak harus wah, yang penting cukup semoga lebih)

snippet.title: The Coldest Village on Earth (Lost My Health for This Video) -71°C, -96°F
snippet.description:
Use the coupon code RUHI29 to buy the MyHeritage DNA kit for only $29/€29/£29 https://bit.ly/RuhiCenet_MH or start your family tree with a 14-day free trial.

Here is my friend's video:
Journey to the World's Coldest Village: Oymyakon at -71°C https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w6fyb46Z-SM
Don't forget to check out "The Ulengovs" channel: https://www.youtube.com/@TheUlengovs

Thanks to MyHeritage for sponsoring this video.

Imagine a village where temperatures drop as low as -71°C, -96°F. Here, spending just a few extra minutes outside can lead to frostbite, the loss of a limb, or even end of life.

I’m in the coldest inhabited place on Earth, at the coldest time of the year. This is Oymyakon. Just to stay alive, I’m wearing more than 20 layers of clothing, weighing nearly 14 kilos. Stepping outside from a warm 30°C home means facing a temperature drop of over 100 degrees. That’s why I’m also wearing gloves, boots, pants, and a coat, all made from reindeer fur. And even that’s not enough. And now, I’m about to show you what life is like when simply going outside becomes a battle for survival.

The cold doesn't just affect people and wild animals. It stops everything from functioning.  Phones don’t work properly and often shut down. Cars left outside freeze in just a few hours. Since the ground is always frozen, no fruits or vegetables can grow here.

We boarded a plane in Moscow, flying east for seven hours to Yakutsk. From there, we covered an 18 hour, 900 kilometer road trip. When we stepped out of the car, it felt like we were on another planet. The hairs in our nose were frozen, and we felt them prick with every breath. The dry air makes us cough uncontrollably.  

Oymyakon is home to around 800 people, spread across 1.5 square kilometers. Seeing anyone else outside is almost impossible, the village feels like it has been abandoned.

snippet.title: Latihan Perdana PERSIB di Lapangan Pendamping, Bersama Skuat Baru | Training Session
snippet.description:
PERSIB menggelar sesi latihan perdana usai libur panjang kompetisi di Lapangan Pendamping Stadion Gelora Bandung Lautan Api (GBLA), Senin 30 Juni 2025. Sesi latihan perdana langsung dipimpin pelatih Bojan Hodak.

Beberapa rekrutan anyar PERSIB sudah bergabung pada sesi latihan perdana ini. Mereka adalah Uilliam Barros, Alfeandra Dewangga, William Marcilio, Saddil Ramdani, Al Hamra Hehanussa, Luciano Guaycochea, dan Rosembergne “Berguinho” da Silva.

Selain itu, pelatih kiper anyar Pangeran Biru, Mario Jorzic pun sudah langsung turun tangan untuk menggembleng Teja Paku Alam dan kawan-kawan.

snippet.title: NEKAT! SESER IKAN MONSTER DI KOLAM TERBENGKALAI PAKE WARING PANJANG
snippet.description:
Nekat! Seser ikan monster di kolam terbengkalai pake waring panjang sekitar 20 meter.

Di kolam terbengkalai yang sudah ada sejak lama ini aku coba untuk cari ikan sebanyak banyaknya karena menurut informasi banyak sekali jenis ikan bahkan ikan monster yang jadi penghuni kolam terbengkalai ini.

Tadi baru saja aku sudah pasang bubu naga, kemudian aku juga akan ngejala di kolam terbengkalai ini sambil menunggu ikan masuk ke bubu, terakhir aku bakal nekat turun langsung ke kolam terbengkalai tuk seser ikan monster yang terlihat dari berontakan nya pake waring panjang.

Lanjut kami pun coba ngelempar jalan dikolam terbengkalai ini, saat lemparan pertama terlihat ada perlawanan ikan besar masuk dalam jalan dan ternyata lepas saat diangkat.

Alhasil ngejala disini kami hanya mendapatkan ikan sepat, lanjut kami coba nekat mempersiapkan waring panjang untuk seser di kolam terbengkalai.

Saat semua sudah terjun ke kolam terbengkalai dan sudah siap, kami pun mulai perlahan menyeser ikan monster disini alhasil mendapatkan ikan nila babon didalam seser waring kami.

Karena masih menyisakan rasa penasaran akan monster penghuni kolam terbengkalai ini, kami pun dengan nekat menyeser berkali kali hingga terlihat ada ikan monster yang melompati seser waring bahkan ada ikan monster yang numbur badan aku.

Di penyeseran berikutnya kami pun berhasil mendapatkan ikan patin monster yang sudah sangat besar, gak nyangka banget bisa dapet ikan patin sebesar ini saat seser.

Ikan patin monster dan ikan nila babon ini menandakan bahwa memang kolam terbengkalai ini menyimpan potensi yang luar biasa.

Karena hari mulai sore setelah mendapatkan ikan patin super babon, kami pun mengangkat bubu naga yang sudah lama terpasang alhasil mendapatkan ratusan ekor ikan sepat.

Seperti itulah keseruan kami bertualang cari ikan di kolam terbengkalai ini, untuk bubu naga berhasil mendapatkan ikan terbanyak sedangkan seser berhasil mendapatkan ikan terbesar dan bisa dibilang rekor seser ikan terbesar yang pernah kami dapatkan.
